				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>A<br>&lt;&nbsp;30&#37; renal <br>utsöndring</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>A forts.<br>&lt;&nbsp;30&#37; renal <br>utsöndring</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>B<br>30–70&#37; renal <br>utsöndring</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>C<br>&gt;&nbsp;70&#37; renal <br>utsöndring</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Alfentanil</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Amitriptylin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Atorvastatin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Ciklosporin A </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Cisplatin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Citalopram</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Diazepam</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Diklofenak</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Epoetin alfa</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Erytromycin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Felodipin <sup>a</sup> </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Fentanyl <sup>a</sup></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Fenytoin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Fexofenadin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Finasterid</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Flumazenil <sup>a</sup> </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Fluoxetin<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Fluvastatin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Galantamin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Haloperidol</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Ibuprofen </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Indometacin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Itrakonazol </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Karbamazepin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Karvedilol </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Klindamycin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Klorpromazin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Klozapin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Lamotrigin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Levodopa</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Lidokain <sup><a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_19\"><sup>a</sup></a></sup></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Loratadin</div><div class=\"tableLine\">Lorazepam </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Losartan</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&lt;&nbsp;0,01</div><div class=\"ta