tonergt syndrom <span>↑</span></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p>abs<span class=\"tab\"></span> = absorption (kan också beteckna biotillgänglighet)</p><p>biv<span class=\"tab\"></span> = biverkningar</p><p>eff<span class=\"tab\"></span> = effekt</p><p>elim = <span class=\"tab\"></span>elimination (via njurar eller metabolism i levern)</p><p>konc = <span class=\"tab\"></span>koncentration i plasma (orsak oklar)</p><p>met<span class=\"tab\"></span> = metabolism</p><p>utsöndr = <span class=\"tab\"></span>utsöndring i njuren eller gallan</p><p>transp = <span class=\"tab\"></span>transport via aktiv efflux såsom P-glykoprotein </p><p>tub sekr<span class=\"tab\"></span> = tubulär sekretion</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_26\">a. <div class=\"tableLine\">Ej registrerat i Sverige (september 2013).</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
